Sales & Purchase Recordbook

Contact:mqzs55@gmail.com

This App for small businesses to provide simple purchase, sales and warehouse management functions. 
Easy to use, completely free

How to use App?
1. Add your goods in the warehouse, enter name, number, notes, etc.
2. The goods you add will appear in the warehouse with a default margin of 0.
3. Choose goods for purchase or sale.
4. Browse your merchandise purchase and sales records anytime and anywhere.
